{"word":"G2761 - κενῶς - kenōs - ken-oce' - In vain","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κενῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kenōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ken-oce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">In vain</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வீணாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"vainly, in vain"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G2756 - κενός - kenós - ken-os'/2756\">G2756</a>; <i>vainly</i>, that is, <i>to no purpose:</i> - in vain.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2754/2754\">G2754</a>, <a href=\"#/G2755/2755\">G2755</a>, <a href=\"#/G2756/2756\">G2756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2757/2757\">G2757</a>, <a href=\"#/G2758/2758\">G2758</a>, <a href=\"#/G2761/2761\">G2761</a>"}]}